	    		<p>Our website has stringent security measures in place to protect the loss, misuse, unauthorized access, improper use or disclosure, unauthorized modification, alteration of the information under our control, and unlawful destruction or accidental loss. Personal Information that we collect will be stored and backed up securely.</p>

